issue.title: iOS
issue.body:
iOS MVP app done.
Features:
Login/Logout
Functionality with Firebase bridge for Chrome Extension
"OK Hound" support
Dope styling

issue.title: Kenz/security
issue.body:
# Minor changes to ensure that permissions work correctly:
- Added a logout button to the Android app
- Fixed bug in chrome extension where user was only authenticated in the scope of the login/out popup, not in the background js script
- changes to firebase security policy can be seen here: https://remote-hound.firebaseio.com/?page=Security -- they're super basic right now, just check that a user is logged in 

@jamie7132 @aefrem @addieshelley 

I'm :ship: ing without waiting for you people sorry
